::FZ/Shuttles::

FZ looks at Vamprah, the scanners beeping with the detected IGL landing, but he leaves it off till later.

"Follow me. Wheeljack's arriving, I'll take you to him."

He walks out of the room, heading for the docking bay.
~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~
The outer doors of the docking bay open, the two Alliance shuttles flying in and landing, the doors opening. Zardus walks out, Mosquitor behind him and carrying Aelo.

"We're in Predacon base?" Mosquitor asks, looking around. Zardus nods.

"Yes, Mosquitor, we're in the Predacon base."
